data.description: HURRY!!!! There is still time left to take an advantage of Homestead Exemptions! (must close by 12/31/23) Here is your chance! This home is perfect for an Owner occupant or an Investor as there is NO HOA and NO Rental Restrictions! This 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms beauty gracefully sits on handsome over 0.71 acres lot. This Raised ranch offers an open and airy living/family room with high ceilings with beams and cozy fireplace. A separate recreation room which is perfect for entertainment or could be also used as a secondary family room as well and it has a half a bath for your convenience. Separate Dining room with doors leading to your private covered back deck - a Perfect place to relax and enjoy your cup of coffee in the morning before starting your day or perhaps a glass of wine or a cocktail after a long day of work. Master bedroom also features high ceilings with beams; two secondary bedrooms are spacious in size and share a full bathroom which makes it perfect as a roommate floor plan if you are looking for one. Home was just recently renovated including: the entire exterior and interior of the home was freshly painted; ALL New modern light fixtures, including all designers ceiling fans with remote controls; New Luxury vinyl floors throughout except for bedrooms (bedrooms have almost new carpet which was installed just few months ago). Kitchen features white cabinets which were just refinished, all New modern kitchen cabinets door handles; New modern kitchen faucet; New gorgeous white glass backsplash, SS appliances. All bathrooms also have updated modern cabinets door handles, New modern light fixtures, New mirrors, and waterfall modern faucets. The deck was freshly painted, the concrete was freshly painted as well as the retaining wall. Septic tank was serviced and repaired in 11/2022; the water heater and HVAC are only 6 years young as well as retaining wall was redone in 2017; 2-car garage with plenty of storage space as well as plenty of additional parking space. Home is conveniently located with close proximity to dining, shopping, Atlanta Airport, major highways and interstate and other fun attractions. This is truly a place to call HOME! Property taxes do not reflect homestead exemptions.
